(2) The terms “weapons of mass destruction” and “WMD” mean chemical, biological, and nuclear weapons, and chemical, biological, and nuclear materials used in the manufacture of such weapons.

(3) The term “items of proliferation concern” means—(A) equipment, materials, or technology listed in—(i) the Trigger List of the Guidelines for Nuclear Transfers of the Nuclear Suppliers Group;

